{"tid":2452955,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男生去年中環用雪糕筒堵路 今判處18個月感化","createTime":"2021-03-19T06:58:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T12:49:34.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f9005ac1dd84f2888310877d9cac517456394e92","tid":2452955,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T06:58:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14515\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14515&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSt3lGhCGuGi3hvupoSMmYHA%3D&h=a905d655\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14515</a><br />\n<br />\n#觀塘裁判法院第一庭 <br />\n#錢禮主任裁判官 #判刑<br />\n#20200609中環 <br />\n<br />\n簡(20)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：在公眾地方造成阻礙<br />\n<br />\n案情：<br />\n2020年6月9日，在中環畢打街與德輔道中交界無合法權限或解釋，而留下一個警察交通雪糕筒，所佔範圍約0.16平方米，可能對在上述公眾地方的車輛造成不便。<br />\n<br />\n控罪案情大概指被告留下的雪糕筒對一輛城巴造成阻礙。<br />\n<br />\n=========================<br />\n感化報告正面，建議18個月感化，跟隨感化官指示參與不同對更生有助的活動。<br />\n被告家庭背景良好，得到不同人，包括老師的支持，品格良好，學業表現亦良好，有參與不同的青年課外活動。<br />\n<br />\n=======================<br />\n<br />\n🟢18個月感化（遵守感化官的指示去工作和居住,參與對更生有幫助的活動,跟從指示接受心理輔導），$500堂費由保釋金扣除。<br />\n🟢三個月後即2021年6月17日0930觀塘法院第一庭聽進度報告。<br />\n（☂️可留意有無記者影相，可問候手足是否需要遮）"},{"pid":"015dfb3d56d32f0ce797f4d7ba86e6ac465c4d51","tid":2452955,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T06:59:02.000Z","msg":"錢禮多數輕手"},{"pid":"d1878dcee667d00502129aec24c6c82ed2c184a6","tid":2452955,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:01:11.000Z","msg":"哇好大罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警察又破大案"},{"pid":"b12e52ac71c9497e993ef254b16cf28be9f7ae18","tid":2452955,"uid":25945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:03:29.000Z","msg":"過多排劣正屍上訴，判即時入監"},{"pid":"03769529122eb8839e591b941fdeda7afe041667","tid":2452955,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:03:31.000Z","msg":"一個雪糕筒 <br />\n<br />\n講出嚟笑左"},{"pid":"c62be0f62c8df932d087a3799101cc2518398edb","tid":2452955,"uid":274722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:06:08.000Z","msg":"0.16平方米點堵路呀dhlm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a59c8fa61c5da0c41f13fd84c3f07e472dfd11","tid":2452955,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:23:55.000Z","msg":"瘋狂式政治打壓"},{"pid":"6f9b18137008762d7ba7018492954e53e3ad822a","tid":2452955,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:33:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"481dd25617f30a9f5ccb932f30957f56fbad3666","tid":2452955,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:50:14.000Z","msg":"去年6月9日，有網民發起午間舉行《抗爭一周年七區聯合和你lunch》行動，20歲巴裔大學生在中環馬路上留下一個雪糕筒，他早前承認在公眾地方造成阻礙罪，案件今在觀塘裁判法院判刑。主任裁判官錢禮按報告建議，判被告接受18個月感化令，其間須接受心理輔導及參與社區服務。被告另須支付堂費500元。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情指，被告背景良好，學業成績優異，矢志服務社群。辯方透露，被告立志成為老師，服務香港的少數族裔社群。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210319/RVZ6HR2KYBGXBDQ4IW4YKKTO24/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210319%2FRVZ6HR2KYBGXBDQ4IW4YKKTO24%2F&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSt3lGhCGuGi3hvupoSMmYHA%3D&h=1b467275\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210319%2FRVZ6HR2KYBGXBDQ4IW4YKKTO24%2F&h=9da1fe8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210319/RVZ6HR2KYBGXBDQ4IW4YKKTO24/</a>"},{"pid":"8e76debee410ebaba0a058c06380663fd87355cb","tid":2452955,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T08:26:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ea0f323043e722246bb4ece42cf4b11aef9c563","tid":2452955,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T10:04:59.000Z","msg":"主任裁判官錢禮判處 18 個月感化，期間要跟從感化官於讀書及工作方面的指示，如有需要須接受心理輔導。他另須支付 500 元堂費，可於保釋金扣除。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情指被告的報告內容正面，感化官建議他接受 18 個月感化。辯方又透露被告家庭背景良好，學業成績優異且投入社區服務，而現時正就讀大學一年級的被告，有志成為一名老師，服務少數族裔社群等。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%A0-lunch-20-%E6%AD%B2%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%AA%8D%E9%A6%AC%E8%B7%AF%E6%94%BE%E9%9B%AA%E7%B3%95%E7%AD%92-%E5%88%A4-18-%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E6%84%9F%E5%8C%96/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E5%2592%258C%25E4%25BD%25A0-lunch-20-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E6%2594%25BE%25E9%259B%25AA%25E7%25B3%2595%25E7%25AD%2592-%25E5%2588%25A4-18-%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%2584%259F%25E5%258C%2596%2F&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSt3lGhCGuGi3hvupoSMmYHA%3D&h=0efe8592\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E5%2592%258C%25E4%25BD%25A0-lunch-20-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E6%2594%25BE%25E9%259B%25AA%25E7%25B3%2595%25E7%25AD%2592-%25E5%2588%25A4-18-%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%2584%259F%25E5%258C%2596%2F&h=4666d685\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%A0-lunch-20-%E6%AD%B2%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%AA%8D%E9%A6%AC%E8%B7%AF%E6%94%BE%E9%9B%AA%E7%B3%95%E7%AD%92-%E5%88%A4-18-%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E6%84%9F%E5%8C%96/</a>"},{"pid":"bda0381b9452ff46692f9933e4095ac34b6d512c","tid":2452955,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"c62be0f62c8df932d087a3799101cc2518398